The difference is the AoE active already on the item is VERY easy to appreciate. Putting the MR boost on top of it would not affect the already appreiable active ability.

AoE's on other actives still are fine. {{item:3069}} {{item:3143}} {{item:3800}}
Part of the reason is there is a notification (audible of visual) of the effect, which makes it easy to notice, and appreciate.
